Bedrijfsomschrijving
DHL Supply Chain offers specialized, proven expertise for various industries, such as life sciences and healthcare.
You will work at the Life Sciences & Healthcare Campus in Bijsterhuizen, near Wijchen, Nijmegen, Oss and Arnhem. From the campus, DHL provides conditioned storage and worldwide distribution for pharmaceutical companies that specialize in products used in the treatment of cancer, cardiovascular disease, MS and rare diseases such as Batten disease. It is the responsibility of DHL and their employees to ensure the timely and error-free delivery of medicines and medical devices to hospitals, pharmacies and patients worldwide on a daily basis.
Functieomschrijving
We are not just looking for a warehouse employee, but for someone who wants to contribute to society.Now of course you wonder what this function means? In this position you are busy picking and packing products on a daily basis, which means that you walk along the racks with your list to pack the products and then pack the products neatly and according to legislation at the pack table and prepare them for transport. .We stand for the health of our fellow human beings and therefore work extremely meticulously. We care about connection and improvement. DHL also looks at your qualities and possible career opportunities.How cool is it if you deliver the products to the customers on time and save lives? You will be working in a very pleasant team.
